                <head>No. 613.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Curry</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1887-03-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">March</hi> 10, 1887</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Curry informs the Department that the Government of Spain is willing to
                    extend the duration of the agreement of October 27, until the 30th of June
                    next.</p>
            </div>
